name: Square clones (4/4)
description:
I am a square.
My skin is pink.
I'm only 4 pixels.
I live in an area of 1000 by 1000 pixels.
Inside the area there are surrounding walls of 100 pixel.

I can clone myself.
My clones can be up to 255 pixels.
They are like me, but different.
Cloning myself does not always work.
It took one million tries to create all my clones.
There are so many of them.
They are staying in the same area, but each in his own place.
